        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\n// 获取 HTTP Request 节点的返回结果\nconst results = $input.first().json.hits;\n\n// 将数组中的每个对象转换成 n8n 的 Item 格式\nreturn results.map(item => {\n  return {\n    json: item\n  };\n});"
